WritableField_GetValue
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
Module:	<Window=>window/m>
#Line
#Wrap off
Veneer:	<writablefield_get_value>
Syntax:	WritableField_GetValue
#indent

On entry:
#indent 6
{FCode}r0 = flags
r1 = window object Id
r2 = 513
r3 = gadget component Id
r4 = pointer to buffer
r5 = size of buffer
{f}
#indent
On exit:
#indent 6
{FCode}r5 = size of buffer (if r4=0)
     else r4 points to writable value
{f}
#indent
#Wrap
Purpose:	Method gets the text in a writable field.